Check out our video tour of this STUNNING build of New American Plan #260000RVC in Virginia! 🤩🏡⁠ by our friends @rivercitycustomhomes 
⁠
We love all of the contemporary details on this one - just look at that KITCHEN 😍 This plan is full of incredible features & offers an optionally finished 3rd floor!⁠
⁠
Quick Specs 👇⁠
📐 3,569 Sq Ft⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
🛏️ 5-6 Bedrooms⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
🛁 4-5 Bathrooms⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
🚙 2 Car Garage⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
📏54'-4" Wide x 67'-1" Deep⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
 😍 What part are you most excited about?⁠
⁠
🌟LINK IN BIO🌟 or visit www.architecturaldesigns.com/260000RVC to check out the entire album & floor plan!⁠

Okay members of the #adhouseplans fam - this is a bit of a special post:⁠⁠
⁠⁠
This past weekend, Hurricane Ida's path through Louisiana and the surrounding states resulted in devastating losses for many individuals and families, including one of our very talented Louisiana based designers & friend. They are currently navigating the aftermath of this terrible storm, including loss of power.⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Our hearts go out to them and all of the members of these communities, a sentiment we're sure you all share. 💖⁠⁠
⁠⁠
We will be donating $100 from each purchase of plans from the SM portfolio (ie. plans ending in "SM") to Hurricane Ida disaster relief efforts. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Swipe ➡️ to see some of the plans included in this collection👇⁠⁠
⁠⁠
